Package group19.Entities

Class FryCook

java.lang.Object
group19.Entities.Entity
group19.Entities.FryCook
All Implemented Interfaces:
CharacterGraphic, Movable
public class FryCook extends Entity implements CharacterGraphic, Movable
Represents a fry cook which consists of x,y coordinates and its left/right buffered images. One can get its active buffered image and move it given its x,y positions.
